Starring...

00:03:21.960 --> 00:03:23.300
The Olsen Triplet

00:03:23.380 --> 00:03:25.080
Discount Channing Tatum

00:03:25.180 --> 00:03:27.380
Duhhhh

00:03:27.380 --> 00:03:29.380
Crysenberg

00:03:29.440 --> 00:03:32.140
and Real Kaiju Have Curves.

00:03:32.150 --> 00:03:35.109
Godzilla. The Good One.

00:03:39.320 --> 00:03:44.420
Man, if that's what his breath is like, I'd
hate to see his farts.

